      <h1 class='title'>Ministerial Cars</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c216WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_216ws' title='Col. 216WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c216WS' name='column_216ws' href='#column_216ws' rel='bookmark'>216WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-05910'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_11'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-norman-baker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_11' title='Link to this speech by Mr Norman Baker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-norman-baker" title="Mr Norman Baker">Norman Baker</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-05910">To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office (1) what the average cost per Minister arising from the allocation of a ministerial car was in each of the last three years; [89072]</p><p id="S6CV0397P0-05911">(2) how many Ministers are entitled to the allocation of a car; and how many Ministers in each year from 1997 have chosen not to avail themselves of one; [89073]</p><p id="S6CV0397P0-05912">(3) what assessment he has made of the practicality of replacement by a car pool of the system of allocation of cars individually to Ministers; and if he will estimate the savings which would result were such a scheme implemented. [89071]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-05913'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_12'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-douglas-alexander' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_12' title='Link to this speech by Mr Douglas Alexander' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-douglas-alexander" title="Mr Douglas Alexander">Mr. Alexander</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-05913">The responsibility for the provision of ministerial cars and drivers has been delegated under the terms of the Framework Document to the Government Car Despatch Agency. I have asked its chief executive Mr Nick Matheson to write to the hon. Member. Copies of his letter will be placed in the Libraries of the House.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
